SUMMARY:Weekly Plan and Tasks
DESCRIPTION:Plan this week's execution. Tasks:\n1) Monday: select 10 prospects and send first-touch outreach.\n2) Wednesday: send follow-up 1 to day-3 non-responders.\n3) Friday: send follow-up 2 to day-7 non-responders.\n4) Friday: run weekly outreach review and refresh next-week list.\n5) Friday: update pre-scale operator scorecard and proof asset progress.
DTSTART:20260518T130000Z
DTEND:20260518T133000Z
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=MO
END:VEVENT

